{"tid":1102811,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"原來沒有 從來都沒有","createTime":"2019-04-12T03:38:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T10:36:44.000Z","uid":193900,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a7647f85e300643bd1beb4c9c33f3127cfbe26c1","tid":1102811,"uid":193900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T03:38:02.000Z","msg":"原來你一直問關於我嘅野係對我冇意思嘅<br />\n原來你經常望著對我笑我係對我冇意思嘅<br />\n原來你因爲我嬲你啲friend係對我冇意思嘅<br />\n原來你講你第一次見到我比我吸引住都係冇意思嘅。     <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你怎樣看 亦像凝望我<br />\n那種不經意 卻洩露矛盾更多<br />\n怎可能 無聊之過<br />\n平常稀疏 只因我心多<br />\n你守護我 但又迴避我<br />\n卻整天吸引著我 注意力無處去躲<br />\n不管如何 有人如此愛我<br />\n我亦暗裡練習 如和你告白講什麼"},{"pid":"5efff1adebc56bc56ff6d490368443b243e608dd","tid":1102811,"uid":168619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T03:49:09.000Z","msg":"好撚MK"},{"pid":"19a7abc8e43d79888a452bb5b9a70e7e9176f124","tid":1102811,"uid":193900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5efff1adebc56bc56ff6d490368443b243e608dd","tid":1102811,"uid":168619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T03:49:09.000Z","msg":"好撚MK"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:10:08.000Z","msg":"好hurt <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895bd767010c57465adb2700ba10183d33c2972f","tid":1102811,"uid":171098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:48:02.000Z","msg":"詳細講來聽下"},{"pid":"b0ae7ffcfbe0bbe04e57fd0ec4990cc92430e69e","tid":1102811,"uid":193900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"895bd767010c57465adb2700ba10183d33c2972f","tid":1102811,"uid":171098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:48:02.000Z","msg":"詳細講來聽下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:06:42.000Z","msg":"同首歌